{"tid":1854031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（最新）支那確診近萬宗武漢肺炎 超過200人死亡","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T10:00:27.000Z","uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae387d6ca3261262b5cf1295378312064df74d0","tid":1854031,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"世衞將疫情列國際公共衛生緊急事件　全國近萬宗確診<br />\n<br />\n全國至今確診接近9700宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎病例，超過200人死亡。世界衛生組織開會後宣布，將疫情列為國際公共衛生緊急事件。中國衛健委與外交部都表示，有信心及能力戰勝疫情。中方又決定盡快派包機，將在海外的武漢公民接載回國。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-31 17:35:10"},{"pid":"0511a08ef8d94fd9375428309a7956c719f5d41e","tid":1854031,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xk8WqoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxk8WqoZ.jpg&h=78a5bbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇傳媒及出版嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n組織工會 全面罷工</span></span><br />\n【港人自救，全民防疫】行動<br />\n - 問卷 - <a href=\"https://forms.gle/8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=b9e04cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/8LUQLEv94tbhxfxe9</a><br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［港共不封關，全港冚家剷］香港傳媒及出版職工會-籌組中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847821\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n又一個工會準備誕生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n路過入黎幫手推個post  謝謝<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ebe177561bdf8a1e11687e36e3833110ac8765dc","tid":1854031,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"Nigga 衛生組織"},{"pid":"007d957da9e18d9f45aecc5d7cf27d69b75a85c7","tid":1854031,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re